last_episode_to_air.name: MADE YOU LOOK
last_episode_to_air.overview: Desperation sets in as Howard tries to evade the Task Force and Ronnie goes on the attack, leaving Raq and Kanan to make some fateful choices. Ronnie changes his identity.

name: Power Book III: Raising Kanan
overview: Set in South Jamaica, Queens, in 1991, this prequel to "Power" revolves around the coming of age of Kanan Stark.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: In Season 4 of "Raising Kanan," the Thomas family finds themselves caught in a web of conflicting loyalties, moral dilemmas, and personal crises that shake the very foundations of their identities. Kanan, still reeling from the death of his partner Ronnie, is determined to seek revenge while forging his own path free from his mother's manipulations. Famous lays low, navigating the dangerous drug game, and Jukebox, now independent from the girl group, embarks on a journey of self-discovery. As their paths converge and diverge, each family member faces a reckoning that will shape their futures and test their bonds.

episodes.name: BACK IN THE DAY
episodes.overview: It's 1991 in South Jamaica, Queens, and 15-year-old Kanan Stark is eager to join his family's growing drug business, led by his mother, "Raquel Raq" Thomas.

episodes.name: REAPING AND SOWING
episodes.overview: After a rival crew member is killed, Raq does whatever is necessary to get the target off Kanan's back.

episodes.name: STICK AND MOVE
episodes.overview: Still reeling from a shocking death, Kanan pushes his way into the drug game with Marvin’s help while Raq plots to take down her competition.

episodes.name: DON'T SLEEP
episodes.overview: All bets are off when a police raid clears out Raq's competition. Promises are broken, secrets are revealed, and revenge is swift.

episodes.name: CHOOSE YOUR BATTLES
episodes.overview: Eager to transform her business after the stash house is hit, Raq overhauls her operation. Meanwhile, Kanan is detained after a fight with Scrappy.

episodes.name: LEVEL UP
episodes.overview: Lou's new artist showcase becomes the nexus of the rivalry between Raq and Unique. At the same time, Kanan cooks up a drug-selling scheme with Marvin.

episodes.name: STAY IN YOUR LANE
episodes.overview: Kanan and Marvin's side hustle goes awry. Raq seeks revenge for the attack on Scrappy. Jukebox suffers a devastating blow.

episodes.name: THE COST OF BUSINESS
episodes.overview: Kanan struggles with a harsh truth after word gets back to Raq that hes behind the bad crack on the streets. Jukebox learns the troubling facts behind Nicoles death. Lou finds himself caught in a crossfire.

episodes.name: LOYAL TO THE END
episodes.overview: As Lou recovers in the hospital, Marvin seeks revenge. Feeling the pressure, Raq turns to Kanan to take out the biggest threat to their family.

episodes.name: PAID IN FULL
episodes.overview: As the situation in the neighborhood turns dire, Raq scrambles to get Kanan out of harm’s way.

episodes.name: THE MORE THINGS CHANGE
episodes.overview: Kanan returns to Queens where Raq is trying to mend the many fractures in the Thomas family. As Raq expands her empire, Kanan doubts his future in the drug game. Meanwhile, Detective Howard is released from the hospital.

episodes.name: MIND YOUR BUSINESS
episodes.overview: Raq learns she may have a snitch and tasks Marvin with confirming the rumor. Lou brings in a potential new artist, but he and Crown disagree. Kanan helps Famous sell mix tapes. Jukebox tracks down her estranged mother.

episodes.name: SLEEPING DOGS
episodes.overview: A surprise encounter with Howard leaves Kanan rattled. Raq tries to expand into new territory, but when an associate and valuables go missing, she is reunited with an old adversary. Lou continues to butt heads with Crown.

episodes.name: PAY THE TOLL
episodes.overview: Kanan and Jukebox search for answers in family matters. When Raq’s push into new territory is stalled, she proposes a meeting. Crown helps Famous get settled. Still investigating Howard’s shooting, Burke questions Unique.

episodes.name: WHAT HAPPENS IN THE CATSKILLS
episodes.overview: Raq focuses on mother-son bonding with Kanan in the Catskills, but they’re interrupted when business follows them. Crown disrespects Lou, bringing their simmering beef to a boil. Burke digs into Howard’s personal life.

episodes.name: IT’S A BUSINESS, MAN
episodes.overview: Raq assures everyone they need to follow orders and keep working as planned. Kanan takes on more responsibility but things go wrong when he runs into neighborhood kids. Lou feels the pressure in his partnership with Crown.

episodes.name: NO LOVE LOST
episodes.overview: Raq searches for a new home. Lou finds himself on the other side of his partner's unpaid debts. Burke gains traction in her investigation on Howard. A botched agreement with Marvin and an associate threatens everything.

episodes.name: A HOUSE IS NOT A HOME
episodes.overview: The rift between Raq and Kanan grows and Kanan seeks comfort elsewhere. Marvin lays low, waiting for the consequences of his actions to blow over. Raq sees dark clouds on the horizon.

episodes.name: ANTI-TRUST
episodes.overview: With his living situation threatened, Famous reaches out to Lou as a last-ditch effort. Raq receives a new business proposal and must eliminate a threat. Burke closes in on what really happened in Baisley Park.

episodes.name: IF Y’DON’T KNOW, NOW Y’KNOW
episodes.overview: Decidedly his own man, Kanan strays further from his mother and sets up shop on his own on the corners of South Jamaica. Worried about retaliation, Raq questions Unique. Lou's rift with Raq grows when he makes a discovery.

episodes.name: HOME SWEET HOME
episodes.overview: Raq makes a life-changing decision in the aftermath of the Mafia’s ambush, but its too little, too late for Kanan, as he looks to pave his own path free of his mother’s lies.

episodes.name: FLIPMODE
episodes.overview: Raq continues her farewell tour with one last job for the Mafia while Kanan dives further into the drug game with an innovative business idea. Howard faces a new threat at the precinct.

episodes.name: OPEN FOR BUSINESS
episodes.overview: As paranoia sets in for Raq and Howard over the Task Force, Kanan and Famous launch their weed delivery business, Jukebox prepares for her audition, and Ronnie grows impatient with Unique.

episodes.name: IN SHEEP'S CLOTHING
episodes.overview: New business ventures take shape for the Thomas family, but the outlook is bleaker for the Mathis brothers as Ronnie’s patience runs out. Raq makes a risky move for Kanan’s obedience.

episodes.name: BROTHERS AND KEEPERS
episodes.overview: Tension between Ronnie and Unique comes to a head while Kanan clashes with both Raq and Famous. Juke bonds with her bandmate, and Lou works to revitalize Cafe Vous. Howard’s attempt to manipulate the Task Force backfires.

episodes.name: INTO THE DARKNESS
episodes.overview: Dangerous secrets are revealed as Famous unburdens himself to Kanan, and Raq finally tries to make amends with Lou. Marvin struggles with his role as stage dad, and Howard attempts to get closer to the Task Force.

episodes.name: WHERE ALL ARE GUILTY
episodes.overview: Lou’s drinking creates a problem for the whole family when Shantel goes looking for justice. Kanan assimilates into Ronnie’s crew, and Raq formulates a new plan for Unique’s former heroin operation.

episodes.name: RECKONINGS
episodes.overview: As a despondent Lou becomes a liability for the family, Raq and Marvin work to get the new heroin operation up and running amidst new competition from Kanan and Ronnie.

episodes.name: HOME TO ROOST
episodes.overview: Ronnie and Kanan’s feud with Raq intensifies as Marvin desperately searches for Lou. Famous and Jukebox both find themselves at potential turning points in their music careers.

episodes.name: MADE YOU LOOK
episodes.overview: Desperation sets in as Howard tries to evade the Task Force and Ronnie goes on the attack, leaving Raq and Kanan to make some fateful choices. Ronnie changes his identity.
